					<h2><a href="http://www.loper-os.org/?p=1475" title="Trilema 2014">Trilema 2014</a></h2>
					
					<div class="entry">
					
						<div class="postmetadata">
							Published on&#58;   Saturday April 26 2014						</div>
						
						<p>I had the honour of being invited to <a href="http://trilema.com/2013/the-conference-second-edition/">Trilema 2014</a> in <a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Timi%C8%99oara">Timișoara</a> - <span style="font-size: 13px;">where I exhibited a few completed </span><a style="font-size: 13px;" href="http://www.loper-os.org/?p=1427">gadgets</a>.</p>
<div class="wp-caption aligncenter" style="width: 570px"><a href="http://www.loper-os.org/wp-content/tri1.jpg"><img class="  " title="Popescu &amp; mike_c" src="http://www.loper-os.org/wp-content/tri1.jpg" alt="Mircea Popescu - friend, co-author, host of the party." width="560" height="420" /></a><p class="wp-caption-text">Left: Mircea Popescu - friend, my project co-author, host of the party.  RNG is running.</p></div>
<div class="wp-caption aligncenter" style="width: 570px"><a href="http://www.loper-os.org/wp-content/tri3.jpg"><img class="  " title="also Popescu &amp; mike_c" src="http://www.loper-os.org/wp-content/tri3.jpg" alt="Popescu - helping me tell the story behind the exhibits." width="560" height="420" /></a><p class="wp-caption-text">Popescu - helping to tell the story behind the exhibits.  And happily philosophizing about many other things.</p></div>
<div class="wp-caption aligncenter" style="width: 570px"><a href="http://www.loper-os.org/wp-content/tri2.jpg"><img class="  " title="various people" src="http://www.loper-os.org/wp-content/tri2.jpg" alt="Audience - other guests, who can name themselves if they feel like it." width="560" height="420" /></a><p class="wp-caption-text">Audience - other guests, who can name themselves if they feel like it.</p></div>
<p><a href="http://trilema.com/2014/ca-tot-s-a-tras-tot-s-a-fumat-tot-s-a-baut-tot-cum-e-peste-tot-la-fel-ca-peste-tot">More pictures at Mr. P&#8217;s site.</a></p>
						
